			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

			<p align="justify">This privacy policy governs your use of the website www.pouch-app.com ("Website") and the software application Pouch! (“Application”) for mobile devices that was created by Pouch, Inc. The Website and Application allow users to store & access any “deals” or “special” offers that they may store via our online web application. </p>

			<h2>What information does the Website and Application obtain and how is it used?</h2>

			<h3>User Provided Information </h3>

			<p align="justify">The Website and Application obtains the information you provide when you sign up on the website or download and register the Application. Registration with us is optional. However, please keep in mind that you may not be able to use some of the features offered by the Website and Application unless you register with us.</p>

			<p align="justify">When you register with us and use the Website or Application, you generally provide (a) your name, Facebook picture, time zone, and other registration information; (b) transaction-related information, such as when you click through to a 3rd party site, respond to any offers, or download or use applications from us; (c) information you provide us when you contact us for help; (d) information you enter into our system when using the Website or Application.</p>

			<p align="justify">We may also use the information you provided us to contact your from time to time to provide you with important information, required notices and marketing promotions.</p>

			<h3>Automatically Collected Information </h3>

			<p align="justify">In addition, the Website and Application may collect certain information automatically, including, but not limited to, the type of desktop or mobile device you use, the device token supplied by Apple (Application only), the IP address of your desktop or mobile device, your desktop or mobile operating system, the type of desktop or mobile Internet browsers you use, and information about the way you use the Website or Application. </p>

			<h2>Does the Website or Application collect precise real time location information of the device?</h2>

			<p align="justify">Neither the Website nor Application does not collect precise information about your location. </p>

			<h2>Do third parties see and/or have access to information obtained by the Website or Application?</h2>

			<p align="justify">Only aggregated, anonymized data is periodically transmitted to external services to help us improve the Website, Application, and our service. We will share your information with third parties only in the ways that are described in this privacy statement.</p>

			<p align="justify">We may disclose User Provided and Automatically Collected Information:</p>

